{"tid":2109120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【刁燈】中國單日採購美國玉米創新高","createTime":"2020-07-15T04:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T14:57:39.000Z","uid":19552,"like":153,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"b0467bb62e7b413c91a949a34a6cdc570dfb499f","tid":2109120,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"在中國與美國緊張關係加劇之際，中國周二錄得有記錄以來最大單日美國玉米採購規模，這是不到一周內第二筆大規模的玉米採購。<br />\n<br />\n美國農業部引述民間出口商報告稱，中國購買176.2萬噸玉米，準備由9月1日開始的2020/21銷售年度付運。農業部數據顯示，此次玉米銷售打破1994年12月創下的145萬噸玉米單日銷售紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n美國農業部早前上周五(10日)宣布，向中國出售136.5萬噸玉米，將在兩個市場年內付運。<br />\n在今年1月與美國簽署的第一階段貿易協議中，中方同意在未來兩年內購買800億美元的美國農產品。"},{"pid":"3a3cc5b23b869bd1576bb359b68be9db9f90f849","tid":2109120,"uid":54373,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d42a70f3860880cd5518a7465fd868b7e8ca47","tid":2109120,"uid":155095,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"美國因武肺嘅經濟損失，中國買多多大豆粟米都補唔返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b232bac6c55cc8310f7a53f7f97a2fc34e2a5140","tid":2109120,"uid":76063,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"玉米刁反擊左美國未?"},{"pid":"2784dda60cc4bb0b9970b770391e9904b9729943","tid":2109120,"uid":82935,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"加價都要買啦， 唔買唔通食草咩<br />\n田又浸晒， 葉又俾蟲食晒"},{"pid":"58bc6d972f0d78fcda34c96697cbf023e9b6ec84","tid":2109120,"uid":63157,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"制裁手段<br />\n買撚哂佢"},{"pid":"f6d512d6efa83dc3fb668970f50d799ff56f6238","tid":2109120,"uid":72009,"like":11,"dislike":35,"score":-24,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"玉米trump，新名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f082ac1adfaeefc33d6b49d9a